deregisterForVAT.title = Deregister for VAT
deregisterForVAT.p1 = You can deregister from VAT if the business no longer needs to submit VAT Returns. We will review your reasons for deregistering within 3 weeks.
deregisterForVAT.p2 = If the business needs to deregister from any other taxes or schemes, you must do this separately.

deregistrationReason.title = Why is the business deregistering from VAT?
deregistrationReason.reason.ceased = It has stopped trading
deregistrationReason.reason.belowThreshold = Annual turnover is below £83,000
deregistrationReason.reason.other = Other

deregistrationDate.title = Does the business want to choose its own deregistration date?
deregistrationDate.p1 = The deregistration date can be up to a maximum of 3 months from today.
deregistrationDate.p2 = We will confirm the deregistration date when your deregistration request is accepted.
deregistrationDate.error.date.invalidDate = Enter a real deregistration date
deregistrationDate.error.date.past = The deregistration date must be in the future
deregistrationDate.error.date.future = The deregistration date must not be more than 3 months from today

deregistrationProperty.title = Does the business have any commercial property?
deregistrationProperty.p1 = This includes both land and buildings.

vatAccounts.title = How are the business’s VAT accounts prepared?
vatAccounts.accountant = If you have an accountant, ask them what accounting method they use.
vatAccounts.method.standard = Standard accounting
vatAccounts.method.cash = Cash accounting
vatAccounts.description.standard = You record VAT whenever you send or receive an invoice
vatAccounts.description.cash = You record VAT whenever you make or receive a payment
vatAccounts.showMeAnExample = Show me an example
vatAccounts.showMeAnExample.p1 = You invoice someone in March but do not receive the money until June. If you record the VAT on this payment in:
vatAccounts.showMeAnExample.bullet1 = March, then you use standard accounting
vatAccounts.showMeAnExample.bullet2 = June, then you use cash accounting

